    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加这些步骤。我看到还有个特殊字段\"当前价格\"，后面标注了FinTech_FraudDetection，这是什么情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
